              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='26807' id='9' type-v2='text' w='95715' x='714' y='72195'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontsize='16'>Q. what is the distribution of listing price</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;</run>
                  <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Listing prices are evenly distributed throughout the dataset, suggesting there is no dominant price segment. The number of listings remains fairly consistent across different price ranges, indicating a broad variety of accommodation options. However, the highest price range contains the fewest listings, suggesting that premium-priced accommodations are less common than lower- and mid-priced options.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
                  <format attr='margin' value='4' />
                </zone-style>
              </zone>
            </zone>
