          <zone forceUpdate='true' h='38029' id='5' type-v2='text' w='98572' x='714' y='60973'>
            <formatted-text>
              <run bold='true' fontsize='16'>Q.how are different types of room distributed?</run>
              <run>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Entire home/apartment listings are the most common accommodation type in the dataset, followed closely by private rooms. Shared rooms and hotel rooms represent only a very small proportion of total listings. This indicates that the Airbnb market is primarily driven by entire-property rentals and private accommodations, while shared and hotel-style options have relatively low availability.</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <zone-style>
              <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
              <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
              <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
